<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>数据隔离 - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E9%9A%94%E7%A6%BB/</link><description>数据隔离 - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E9%9A%94%E7%A6%BB/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>MyBatis-Plus多租户</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/java%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6/mybatis-plus%E5%A4%9A%E7%A7%9F%E6%88%B7/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/java%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6/mybatis-plus%E5%A4%9A%E7%A7%9F%E6%88%B7/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="mybatis-plus多租户">MyBatis-Plus多租户</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：MyBatis-Plus通过TenantLineInnerInterceptor实现SQL级多租户隔离，在ORM层自动拼接租户ID条件，相比独立数据库和共享数据库独立Schema方案，是成本和隔离性最均衡的SaaS数据隔离方案。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="mybatis-plus多租户通过拦截器自动改写sql在应用层实现行级数据隔离">MyBatis-Plus多租户通过拦截器自动改写SQL，在应用层实现行级数据隔离</h2>
<h3 id="多租户方案对比">多租户方案对比</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>方案</th>
          <th>隔离级别</th>
          <th>成本</th>
          <th>复杂度</th>
          <th>适用场景</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>独立数据库</td>
          <td>物理隔离</td>
          <td>高</td>
          <td>低</td>
          <td>大客户定制、强合规要求</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>共享数据库独立Schema</td>
          <td>逻辑隔离</td>
          <td>中</td>
          <td>中</td>
          <td>中大型企业客户</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>共享Schema行级隔离</td>
          <td>行级隔离</td>
          <td>低</td>
          <td>高</td>
          <td>中小客户SaaS</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
